- Much of this week has been focused on recovering from last week. Furnace Fest was awesome[1] but I brought home a festival flu ("acute sinusitis") in addition to the rather-expected festival fatigue. I got some drugs on Friday and started to feel a lot better (and my COVID-free streak continues!).
